data.description:
Ask about $6000 SELLER PAID Closing Cost or Upgrades to customize! Come see Mount Holly's Riverfront Neighborhood nestled along the banks of the picturesque Catawba River. This Riverfront 3-bedroom, 4-bathroom townhome, featuring a delightful semi-open floorplan with high ceilings has a prime location. You'll relish the BONUS living space, covered patio, paved deck and the convenience of a dedicated parking garage.  It features stainless steel appliances, upgraded ceiling fans, generous closet space and a spa-like owner's suite bathroom designed for ultimate relaxation. 
This is your chance to experience fantastic amenities, spacious floor plans, and an unbeatable location close to the airport, shopping, delectable dining, and bustling Charlotte. Enjoy access to the Tailrace Marina, food from J.R. Cash's Grill & Bar, and quick access to The Stowe Family.
